OL,3,CSenedd members' pay set to rise as
OL,4,Clowest-paid staff face cuts
OL,6,FThe pay of politicians in Cardiff Bay
OL,7,Fis set to rise while some of the
OL,8,FSenedd's lowest-paid support staff
OL,9,Fface cuts, the Welsh Parliament's pay
OL,10,Fbody confirmed.
OL,12,FSenedd members, who receive a basic
OL,13,Fsalary of #76,380 after a #4,300 rise
OL,14,Fin 2025, are set to receive another
OL,15,Fincrease in 2026 linked to a Welsh
OL,16,Faverage earnings index.
