OL,3,CSenedd members' pay set to rise as
OL,4,Clowest-paid staff face cuts
OL,6,FBut the Senedd's remuneration board,
OL,7,Fwhich decides politicians' pay, also
OL,8,Fconfirmed the top end of the lowest
OL,9,Fpay grade for support staff will be
OL,10,Fcut by almost #1,300 to #32,414.
OL,12,FThe Unite and PCS unions, as well as
OL,13,Fthe Plaid Cymru group, opposed the cut
OL,14,Fto the maximum salary for the lowest
OL,15,Fpay band. Some affected staff will be
OL,16,Foffered two years' pay protection
OL,17,Fwhich Unite warned is not enough.
