OL,3,CSenedd members' pay set to rise as
OL,4,Clowest-paid staff face cuts
OL,6,FThe board justified the change based
OL,7,Fon benchmarking and ensuring alignment
OL,8,Fwith market rates of similar
OL,9,Fcomplexity and responsibility. But the
OL,10,Fboard's own impact assessment
OL,11,Frecognised the cut may have an adverse
OL,12,Fimpact on women and disabled people.
OL,14,FMost members of staff will be
OL,15,Fpositively impacted by the reforms,
OL,16,Fthe board said, with the highest pay
OL,17,Fpoints for bands one and two, senior
OL,18,Fadvisers, and chiefs of staff
OL,19,Fincreasing.
