OL,3,CSenedd members' pay set to rise as
OL,4,Clowest-paid staff face cuts
OL,6,FThe board's year-long review, which
OL,7,Fcost more than #115,000 in consultancy
OL,8,Ffees alone, concludes as the Senedd is
OL,9,Fset to expand from 60 to 96
OL,10,Fpoliticians at May's election.
OL,12,FSenedd members who hold additional
OL,13,Foffices such as committee chairs and
OL,14,Fthe first minister will also pocket
OL,15,F#15,514 to #90,701 extra a year for
OL,16,Ftheir roles, on top of their #76,380
OL,17,Fsalary.
