OL,4,Clowest-paid staff face cuts
OL,6,FThe salaries and additional payments
OL,7,Fwill be subject to a rise in line with
OL,8,FNovember's latest ASHE Wales earnings
OL,9,Findex, which stood at 6% last year.
OL,11,FElizabeth Hayward, who chairs the
OL,12,Fremuneration board, said: "Fair pay is
OL,13,Fessential to a representative Senedd.
OL,14,FIt's a demanding and vitally important
OL,15,Frole.
