OL,6,F"And the support provided to members
OL,7,Fhelps them work in their
OL,8,Fconstituencies and in the Senedd,
OL,9,Freducing barriers to ensure the Senedd
OL,10,Fcan reflect Welsh society, so anyone `
OL,11,Fno matter their background or
OL,12,Fcircumstances ` can become a Member of
OL,13,Fthe Senedd.
OL,15,F"The board has carefully considered
OL,16,Fall of its decisions for salaries and
OL,17,Fbudgets which are linked to average
OL,18,Fearnings measures and inflation."
