OL,3,CSenedd members' pay set to rise as
OL,4,Clowest-paid staff face cuts
OL,6,FThe board, which removed a 3% cap on
OL,7,Frises in politicians' pay in 2025,
OL,8,Frejected Plaid Cymru calls for chief
OL,9,Fwhips to receive an additional salary.
OL,11,FThe board also raised the amount
OL,12,FSenedd members can claim for office
OL,13,Fstart-up costs, such as buying
OL,14,Ffurniture and redecorating, by 30% to
OL,15,F#6,500. Those who choose to keep the
OL,16,Fsame office following the election
OL,17,Fwill receive up to #2,500 for a
OL,18,Frefresh.
