OL,3,CSenedd members' pay set to rise as
OL,4,Clowest-paid staff face cuts
OL,6,FMembers will be able to claim a
OL,7,F#27,430 yearly budget, pegged against
OL,8,Fthe Consumer Price Index, for office
OL,9,Frunning costs ` regardless of whether
OL,10,Fthey have a constituency office.
OL,12,FPoliticians who work exclusively from
OL,13,Fthe Senedd office in Cardiff Bay could
OL,14,Fonly claim up to #11,205 a year
OL,15,Fbefore, but this limit will be removed
OL,16,Fdue to an increase in remote working.
