OL,3,CSenedd members' pay set to rise as
OL,4,Clowest-paid staff face cuts
OL,6,FThe board, which has annual costs of
OL,7,Fmore than #500,000 according to latest
OL,8,Faccounts, said giving all members the
OL,9,Fsame office budget provides maximum
OL,10,Fflexibility and simplicity.
OL,12,FHalf of the 96 politicians, those who
OL,13,Frepresent the eight new constituencies
OL,14,Ffurthest from the Senedd, will be able
OL,15,Fto claim #12,900 a year for renting a
OL,16,Fsecond home in the Cardiff area.
