OL,3,CSenedd members' pay set to rise as
OL,4,Clowest-paid staff face cuts
OL,6,FThey would also be reimbursed for
OL,7,Fcouncil tax, utility bills and
OL,8,Finsurance after the board decided to
OL,9,Fnearly double the number of
OL,10,Fpoliticians eligible to claim for
OL,11,Fsecond homes.
OL,13,FThe board decided to remove a
OL,14,Fhomeworking allowance for staff
OL,15,Fdespite concerns the change could
OL,16,Fdisproportionately affect women,
OL,17,Fcarers and disabled support staff.
