OL,3,CSenedd members' pay set to rise as
OL,4,Clowest-paid staff face cuts
OL,6,FThe rationale was that the allowance
OL,7,Fwas a temporary measure during the
OL,8,Fpandemic and its removal is consistent
OL,9,Fwith other public bodies which removed
OL,10,Fsimilar provisions years ago.
OL,12,FPoliticians will be able to claim up
OL,13,Fto #1,050 a month to cover the care
OL,14,Fcosts of three dependants out of
OL,15,Fnormal working hours, in a move
OL,16,Fdesigned to remove barriers for those
OL,17,Fwith caring responsibilities.
