OL,3,CSenedd members' pay set to rise as
OL,4,Clowest-paid staff face cuts
OL,6,FSenedd members who relocate to Cardiff
OL,7,Fwith dependants during the working
OL,8,Fweek will also be able to access an
OL,9,Fextra #5,160 a year, up 170% from
OL,10,F#1,905, for accommodation costs.
OL,12,FThe board decided to relax
OL,13,Finternational travel rules but rowed
OL,14,Fback a proposal to scrap a requirement
OL,15,Ffor politicians to submit a business
OL,16,Fcase before. A business case will
OL,17,Fstill be needed for oversight reasons
OL,18,Fbut a requirement to publish a post-
OL,19,Ftrip report will be removed.
