OL,6,FThe way political groups are funded
OL,7,Fwill also change, with the budget no
OL,8,Flonger being a fixed pot of money
OL,9,Fshared between them. Each group will
OL,10,Freceive a set amount per member, with
OL,11,Fparties in government getting about
OL,12,F75% less than opposition parties to
OL,13,Fensure fairness.
